{"surahDetails":{"id":94,"arabicName":"الشرح","banglaName":"বক্ষ প্রশস্তকরণ","englishName":"The Consolation","enTranslatedName":"Ash-Sharh","arLocation":"مكية","enLocation":"meccan","totalWords":27,"totalLetters":102,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio-surah/128/ar.alafasy/94.mp3","totalAyah":8},"surah":{"id":94,"verses":[{"id":1,"arabic_text":"أَلَمۡ نَشۡرَحۡ لَكَ صَدۡرَكَ","bangl_text":"আমি কি আপনার বক্ষ উম্মুক্ত করে দেইনি","english_text":"Did We not expand for you, [O Muhammad], your breast","page":596,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6091.mp3","colorText":"أَلَمْ نَشْرَحْ لَكَ صَ<tajweed class=qalaqah>دْ</tajweed>رَكَ <span class=end>١</span>"},{"id":2,"arabic_text":"وَوَضَعۡنَا عَنكَ وِزۡرَكَ","bangl_text":"আমি লাঘব করেছি আপনার বোঝা","english_text":"And We removed from you your burden","page":596,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6092.mp3","colorText":"وَوَضَعْنَا عَ<tajweed class=ikhafa>نك</tajweed>َ وِزْرَكَ <span class=end>٢</span>"},{"id":3,"arabic_text":"ٱلَّذِيٓ أَنقَضَ ظَهۡرَكَ","bangl_text":"যা ছিল আপনার জন্যে অতিশয় দুঃসহ।","english_text":"Which had weighed upon your back","page":596,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6093.mp3","colorText":"ٱلَّذ<tajweed class=madda_obligatory>ِىٓ</tajweed> أَ<tajweed class=ikhafa>نق</tajweed>َضَ ظَهْرَكَ <span class=end>٣</span>"},{"id":4,"arabic_text":"وَرَفَعۡنَا لَكَ ذِكۡرَكَ","bangl_text":"আমি আপনার আলোচনাকে সমুচ্চ করেছি।","english_text":"And raised high for you your repute","page":596,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6094.mp3","colorText":"وَرَفَعْنَا لَكَ ذِكْرَكَ <span class=end>٤</span>"},{"id":5,"arabic_text":"فَإِنَّ مَعَ ٱلۡعُسۡرِ يُسۡرًا","bangl_text":"নিশ্চয় কষ্টের সাথে স্বস্তি রয়েছে।","english_text":"For indeed, with hardship [will be] ease","page":596,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6095.mp3","colorText":"فَإِ<tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>َ مَعَ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْعُسْرِ يُسْرًا <span class=end>٥</span>"},{"id":6,"arabic_text":"إِنَّ مَعَ ٱلۡعُسۡرِ يُسۡرٗا","bangl_text":"নিশ্চয় কষ্টের সাথে স্বস্তি রয়েছে।","english_text":"Indeed, with hardship [will be] ease","page":596,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6096.mp3","colorText":"إِ<tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>َ مَعَ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْعُسْرِ يُسْرًا <span class=end>٦</span>"},{"id":7,"arabic_text":"فَإِذَا فَرَغۡتَ فَٱنصَبۡ","bangl_text":"অতএব, যখন অবসর পান পরিশ্রম করুন।","english_text":"So when you have finished [your duties], then stand up [for worship]","page":596,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6097.mp3","colorText":"فَإِذَا فَرَغْتَ فَ<tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed><tajweed class=ikhafa>نص</tajweed>َ<tajweed class=qalaqah>بْ</tajweed> <span class=end>٧</span>"},{"id":8,"arabic_text":"وَإِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ فَٱرۡغَب","bangl_text":"এবং আপনার পালনকর্তার প্রতি মনোনিবেশ করুন।","english_text":"And to your Lord direct [your] longing","page":596,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6098.mp3","colorText":"وَإِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ فَ<tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>رْغَ<tajweed class=qalaqah>ب</tajweed> <span class=end>٨</span>"}]}}